Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.45,0:00:50.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我这种小人物纠缠合适吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.61,0:00:55.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事态似乎愈发严重了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.12,0:00:57.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少看不起我们
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.32,0:01:03.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙也能应付吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.24,0:01:08.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可…可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.96,0:01:17.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.11,0:01:24.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要死了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.44,0:01:29.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死在这里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.70,0:01:36.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个无趣的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.18,0:01:48.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就借你点…力量
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.33,0:01:50.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,力量
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.11,0:02:06.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要控制…力量
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.31,0:02:11.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,力量的…控制…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.45,0:02:14.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.72,0:02:21.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没…结束
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.36,0:02:19.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定能做到的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.34,0:02:25.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信…你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.29,0:04:51.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看招
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.72,0:04:54.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.73,0:04:57.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但不是九尾化
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.35,0:05:01.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.43,0:05:08.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃掉了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.27,0:05:11.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.77,0:05:16.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多克先生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.34,0:05:21.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里很危险 抓紧去避难吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.77,0:05:24.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…如果不制止那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.89,0:05:32.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了 请交给我们…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.91,0:05:37.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我虽然被解雇了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.64,0:05:39.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但曾经也是村子的守卫
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.37,0:05:43.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保护这里…保护巨坑…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.93,0:05:46.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我的责任
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.07,0:05:52.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.33,0:05:57.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一个人可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.84,0:05:59.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以 太危险了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.55,0:06:02.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凭哥哥现在的体力
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.78,0:06:04.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能抵达目的地吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.98,0:06:10.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了…带我一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.57,0:06:15.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.10,0:06:18.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你别去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.46,0:06:19.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.88,0:06:21.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.67,0:06:22.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.37,0:06:55.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法兹 不可以再挑食了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.59,0:06:57.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算难吃也不能挑肥拣瘦哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.83,0:07:01.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要增强体力 保护大家
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.89,0:07:09.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兰德 你最大 要振作起来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.45,0:07:13.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家有困难要互相帮助哦 加油
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.68,0:07:19.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小空 要好好照顾大家哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.14,0:07:22.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照看好米娜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.76,0:07:27.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷欧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.11,0:07:32.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今后或许会经历很多酸甜苦辣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.22,0:07:35.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要做大家的支柱哦 加油
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.46,0:07:43.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米娜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.40,0:07:48.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你了 米娜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.22,0:07:52.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时扇了你一记耳光 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.28,0:07:57.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明只有米娜察觉到鸣人哥哥的异样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.93,0:08:01.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没能理解你…对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.42,0:08:05.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后也许会很辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.71,0:08:09.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 不要逃避 坚强起来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.92,0:08:12.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和哥哥还有大家一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.03,0:08:15.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坚强地活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.40,0:08:32.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然只是短暂的时光
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.44,0:08:34.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但和大家在一起真的很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.56,0:08:37.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是相当幸福的时光啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.26,0:08:39.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢大家
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.08,0:08:42.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.12,0:08:45.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我爱你们
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.91,0:08:48.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我爱你们
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.75,0:08:59.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诸位 孩子们就拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.16,0:09:02.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们会全力以赴的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.72,0:09:04.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希塞露
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.36,0:09:12.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希塞露姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.82,0:09:13.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.66,0:09:34.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.47,0:09:42.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.59,0:09:45.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能死里逃生的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.69,0:09:48.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能活下来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.60,0:09:50.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们就结婚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.78,0:10:15.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于说出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.16,0:10:19.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那无论如何都要活下去哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.63,0:11:24.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了 是音律
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.87,0:11:29.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据那家伙说是按特定顺序排列的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.73,0:11:30.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么样的顺序呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.88,0:11:31.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.95,0:11:57.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 就是米娜哼得曲子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.07,0:12:04.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子很早前就一直哼着的曲子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.27,0:12:29.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斩尽 杀绝…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.48,0:12:31.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将这世界的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.99,0:12:49.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样一定…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.34,0:12:53.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.62,0:13:06.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.89,0:13:11.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕 完全失去自我了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.97,0:13:13.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.20,0:13:47.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希塞露
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.03,0:13:50.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希塞露
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.63,0:14:16.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快爬上来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.77,0:14:20.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 好像脱臼了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.05,0:14:27.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小樱 快帮我治疗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.33,0:14:29.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.46,0:14:49.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.33,0:14:52.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么 可是九尾的力量太强了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.62,0:14:54.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道能束缚它多久
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.17,0:15:10.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很辛苦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.90,0:15:12.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米娜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.05,0:15:35.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行了 得赶紧想其他办法
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.92,0:16:08.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别认输
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.84,0:16:21.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥 够了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.95,0:16:26.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经有准备了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.96,0:16:29.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我决不会放手的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.14,0:16:31.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.79,0:16:34.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起我来 还是赶紧让天之矛停下来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.73,0:16:35.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,决不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.60,0:16:40.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我再次看着最爱之人落下…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.75,0:16:42.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,决不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.65,0:16:49.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直 一直 一直都喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.44,0:16:51.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才拼命抓住你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.12,0:16:54.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.44,0:16:59.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我再也不会放手了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.81,0:17:04.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果放手的话 还不如一起掉下去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.33,0:17:07.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是从那时起对你念念不忘的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.97,0:17:11.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算我比你高
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.39,0:17:15.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你变秃 变胖 变得迟钝 变得懦弱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.81,0:17:17.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你对我敬而远之
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.60,0:17:21.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便如此 我还是一直喜欢着你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.62,0:17:31.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 谁去保护那些孩子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.93,0:17:34.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有靠你了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.42,0:17:39.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些孩子的未来只有靠你拯救了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.62,0:17:41.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.07,0:18:15.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了 帮助我们
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.29,0:18:19.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要守护 想要帮助
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.03,0:18:23.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最重要的人们 我的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.12,0:18:32.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮助爸爸和妈妈…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.09,0:18:35.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相信着 相信着
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.56,0:18:38.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相信正义的力量 相信你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.88,0:18:40.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸣人哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.42,0:18:41.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.58,0:18:42.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救救…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.14,0:18:44.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.17,0:18:48.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸和妈妈…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.63,0:19:06.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拯救世界吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.44,0:19:10.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保护好那些孩子们
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.49,0:19:15.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱着你…爱着你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.60,0:19:19.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最重要的…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.39,0:20:12.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸣…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.29,0:20:13.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.69,0:20:16.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔 赶紧阻止那个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.97,0:20:36.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少捣乱…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.30,0:22:41.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸣人哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.19,0:23:25.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸣人哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.02,0:23:40.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好重啊 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.02,0:23:50.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你救我一命 鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.40,0:23:53.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢 真的感激不尽
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.79,0:23:23.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,还没完
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.25,0:23:27.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,竟然用秽土转生让人柱力们复活
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.31,0:23:28.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,我决饶不了你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.38,0:23:31.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,这场战争由我来阻止
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.99,0:23:34.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,鸣人能够感知敌意
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.93,0:23:46.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,这样他就必须得出场了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.92,0:23:55.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,果然不出我所料
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.20,0:23:56.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,今日起 千手的火之意志将要消亡
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.38,0:23:58.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,下集 火影忍者疾风传
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.03,0:24:00.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,鸣人 参战
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.60,0:24:02.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,终于轮到我出场了